Introduction
Jelly Truck is a unique and entertaining physics-based driving game developed by XYZ Studios. In this wobbly adventure, players control a jelly-like truck and navigate through challenging levels filled with obstacles and puzzles. With its colorful graphics, bouncy physics, and addictive gameplay, Jelly Truck offers a delightful and gelatinous experience that will keep you engaged for hours.

Gameplay
In Jelly Truck, players take control of a flexible and squishy truck as they maneuver through a variety of imaginative levels. The objective is to reach the end point of each level while overcoming obstacles such as steep hills, gaps, and moving platforms. The unique physics of the jelly truck add an extra layer of challenge and fun to the gameplay.
